content:
There are many species of animals that can be seen on a safari in Kruger National Park, including:

1. African elephants
2. African buffaloes
3. African lions
4. African leopards
5. Black and white rhinoceroses
6. African wild dogs
7. Cheetahs
8. Giraffes
9. Hippopotamuses
10. Zebras
11. Warthogs
12. Impalas
13. Kudus
14. Waterbucks
15. Crocodiles
16. Baboons
17. Monkeys
18. Various species of antelope
19. Different types of birds
